# Title: Audio Capture
# Author: Pawel Mazur, Milad Cheraghi
# Date: 2021-09-04
# Level: low
# Description: Detects attempts to record audio using the arecord and ecasound utilities.
# MITRE Tactic: Collection
# Tags: attack.collection, attack.t1123
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/auditd/lnx_auditd_audio_capture.yml

(a0="arecord" a1="-vv" a2="-fdat" type="EXECVE") OR (SYSCALL="memfd_create" exe="*/ecasound" type="SYSCALL")